Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.25,0:00:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一分為二的月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.92,0:00:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明亮的部分和黑暗的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.50,0:00:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.08,0:00:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.07,0:00:37.63,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}The girl with the sharp thorn in her flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.63,0:00:40.25,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I meet you at your story
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.26,0:00:45.34,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Behind the hatred there lies a murderous love
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.45,0:00:48.02,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Do you kill your friends
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.02,0:00:50.63,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}If you can fulfill your wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.63,0:00:53.25,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Can you die for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:56.35,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}They are synonymous words
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.35,0:00:58.92,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Life is a game  It's a survival  That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.92,0:01:01.51,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}How do you start?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.51,0:01:04.24,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Time and Space  It's a crossroad  through a gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.24,0:01:07.14,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Where do you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.14,0:01:09.62,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}You seek eternal breath
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.69,0:01:11.54,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Why do you need to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.54,0:01:16.91,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We don't know when this world came into being
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:18.78,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We are the timeleaper
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.78,0:01:21.79,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Nothing's gonna change with you in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.79,0:01:24.82,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Everything will be decided by the rules
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.82,0:01:29.63,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Oh,We are traveling the past and the future through love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.63,0:01:30.29,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Break out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.29,0:01:35.34,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Let's dial back all the pains and we will be born again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.34,0:01:37.96,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I wanna see the stars with you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.96,0:01:41.02,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Over the miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:47.83,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It's not a Dead END
