Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.98,0:22:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長這麼大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.07,0:22:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各方面都…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.57,0:22:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.95,0:22:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}很好 把時間倒流回去了
