Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.33,0:22:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有些感動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.62,0:22:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定會成功的！
