Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Deus的核呀 把2nd變小吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.34,0:22:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嬰兒！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.58,0:22:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.79,0:23:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…是由乃…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.51,0:23:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 才幾天沒見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.09,0:23:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長這麼大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.14,0:23:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各方面都…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.74,0:23:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.38,0:23:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}倒回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.98,0:23:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.30,0:23:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有些感動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.83,0:23:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}討厭討厭討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.06,0:23:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.09,0:23:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Deus的核呀 把2nd變小吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.88,0:23:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃你…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.58,0:23:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的胸…變小了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.58,0:23:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住…住手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個是！
